author: COMSOL
description:
This example demonstrates how to use the Lithium-Ion Battery interface for modeling a sodium-ion battery. The geometry is in one dimension and the model is isothermal.

The sodium-ion battery chemistry has many similarities to the lithium-ion battery chemistry, and can often be described by the same equations for charge and mass transport, electrode kinetics, and electrode particle intercalation.
